  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925830/extras/58fe0f12933dffdefe6a9e1ae1e2cbfb.webp?t=1667702989\" width=640 height=62 /></span><br>       李未时是一个新闻记者，有一位相谈多年准备结婚的未婚妻赵倚蝶。一次偶然的机会，李未时得知三年前劈腿的初恋女友林见鹤落下残疾，而对方更是声明是因为被自己抛弃所以才出了车祸，落得如此下场。李未时心存疑虑展开调查，却被神秘组织绑入废弃物理实验室中，危急之时，李未时发现神秘组织和废弃的时间机器实验相关，情急之下启动时间机器，却不料自己因此卷入了一段爱恋与阴谋的轮回纠缠之旅。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925830/extras/23edcad6b02668f690c2e273dc934f65.avif?t=1667702989\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925830/extras/ae1b75f77e07fdec0216d8c98c01a885.webp?t=1667702989\" width=640 height=62 /></span><br>■ 100%视频定制<br>■ 多个结局<br>■ 你的选择决定主角命运<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925830/extras/a831319ffed0d65532496e88a980c9ae.avif?t=1667702989\" width=640 height=350 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925830/extras/2860b17d9d162e9643226382dcab1fc4.webp?t=1667702989\" width=640 height=62 /></span><br>■ 海量谜题<br>■ 趣味烧脑<br>■ 享受全新解谜体验<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925830/extras/ce8246246df6612e2d9820135cbc0694.avif?t=1667702989\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925830/extras/4219eaf3005d3418cbb62597fd741562.webp?t=1667702989\" width=640 height=62 /></span><br>■ 整理线索<br>■ 探寻真相<br>■ 挖掘隐藏在阴谋背后的故事<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item